snippet.title: Tecmo Super Bowl - gameplay and animated scenes (60 fps)
snippet.description:
Some footage from the NES classic "Tecmo Super Bowl".
View at 720p or higher to watch at 60 fps.

Note that the HD versions of the video were upscaled from 480i.
